data.Name: Douglas County presents Josh Turner LIVE with YA'BOYZ After Party
data.Description: NO REFUNDS OR EXCHANGES - RAIN OR SHINE. Josh Turner will be performing Live in Concert! https://joshturner.com/ Following Josh Turner, join us for the Stomp Your Boots After Party, featuring YA'BOYZ performing live! https://www.yaboyzmusic.com/ Located in the Outdoor Arena. Seats are reserved in the stands and general admission on the Outdoor Arena DIRT floor. All guests must have a ticket, including children (NO exceptions) and will be wrist banded on entry. Entire family is welcome! Food and Drinks available for purchase. All bags are subject to security check. No outside alcohol allowed. Alcoholic beverages may be purchased inside grounds.
